data.title: That's Me All Over by Cornelia Otis Skinner
data.meta_description: That's Me All Over by Cornelia Otis Skinner and a great selection of related books, art and collectibles available now at AbeBooks.com.
data.text:
Condition: Good. 1950. Reprint. 312 pages. Green jacket over cloth. B&W illustrations throughout. Notable foxing and tanning to endpapers and page edges. Previous owner's inscription to front endpaper. Mild wear to spine, board edges and corners, with scuffing and marking to boards. Notable sunning to spine and board edges. Clipped dust jacket. Moderate wear, tear and loss to edges and corners. Notable tanning, foxing and soiling to DJ.

Condition: Good. 1949. First Edition Thus. 312 pages. Pictorial jacket over green cloth. Contains black and white illustrations throughout. Pages remain bright and clear, with mild foxing to edges. Binding is firm. Previous owner's inscription to front free endpaper. Boards and spine have minimal shelf-wear, with mild corner bumping and crushing to ends. Noticeable bleach spotting overall. Unclipped jacket. Mild foxing to all surfaces. Heavy edgewear, with visible rips and chipping, and some areas of loss. Moderate marking to exterior.

Hardcover. Condition: Good. Dust Jacket Condition: Fair. Alajalov (illustrator). Corner unclipped, wear to edges and corner of dustjacket, edges and corners creased and worn, some small rips and nicks, top and bottom of spine chipped and worn, some wear to sides of spine, surdace a little grubby, some light wear to covers and spine, corners a little bumped and worn, top and bottom of spine a little bumped and worn, internally in good condition, pages crisp and clear.

Hardcover. Condition: Very Good. Dust Jacket Condition: Good. Publisher - Constable & co, London, 1950. Repr. Originally published 1949. With illustrations by Alajalov. Very good condition, green boards with small areas of sunning where there is jacket loss, silver gilt lettering to spine, corners bumped. A little scattered foxing. No marks or inscriptions. Clipped jacket good condition with chips and tears, especially to top area of spine.
